sense.def:
To fetch something or someone
pomeni iti in pripeljati ali prinesti nekaj ali nekoga od tam, kjer je.

seg.quote: He fetched a bucket of water from the pond.
Scylla ran to fetch her guardian a long cool drink.

sense.def:
Kadar nekaj
fetches a particular amount of money
, je prodano za določen znesek.

seg.quote: His pictures fetch very high prices.

sense.def:
To fetch up somewhere
pomeni nekam priti, navadno nenamenoma;
